Package hu.bme.mit.theta.cat.dsl.gen

Interface CatListener

All Superinterfaces:
org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
All Known Implementing Classes:
CatBaseListener
public interface CatListener extends org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
This interface defines a complete listener for a parse tree produced by CatParser.
